| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2563 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7cda275b-77c6-50d2-8f39-126e7e5ff4fa"
